<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.176294>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. (a) Adult male of L. hermannunezi in life. Specimen collected approximately 8 km E of Los Barros, Laguna del Laja, Chile; (b) adult female from the same locality. Photos J. A. Schulte." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/176294/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.176296>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Holotype of Liolaemus hermannunezi, male, MNHNC 3785, from 10 km E of Los Barros, near Pichachén Pass, Eighth Region, Chile. Photo D. Pincheira-Donoso." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/176296/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.176297>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Map of the North-Western Patagonia of Argentina and Chile, showing the distribution of Liolaemus hermannunezi (black circle), L. rothi (empty circles), L. sagei (cross), and L. loboi (black triangle). Details on the wide Patagonian geographical distribution of L. rothi can be found in Cei (1986)" ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/176297/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

